## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and may not include the most recent findings or developments in climate science. Additionally, the report relies on secondary sources, which may introduce bias or interpretation errors. Further research and primary data analysis are recommended for a more comprehensive understanding of climate change threats.